    <string name="tipdesc1">"Effective study habits make a huge difference in long-term "</string>
    <string name="tipdesc2">"retention. Techniques like Pomodoro (25 min focus, 5 min break), "</string>
    <string name="tipsdesc3">"spaced repetition, and active recall help your brain process and "</string>
    <string name="tipdesc4">"store information more efficiently. Pair these with enough sleep, "</string>
    <string name="tipdesc5">"hydration, and short physical breaks to keep your focus sharp "</string>
    <string name="tipsdesc6">throughout the day.</string>
